query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `user_licenses` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
  `userId` int,
  `organizationId` int,
  `licenseType` enum('direct','partner') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'direct',
  `partnerId` int,
  `activationCodeId` int,
  `status` enum('active','expired','suspended','cancelled') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'active',
  `activatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `expiresAt` timestamp,
  `renewsAt` timestamp,
  `billingCycle` enum('monthly','yearly') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'monthly',
  `price` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'EUR',
  `storeUrl` varchar(500),
  `storePartnerId` int,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX `licenses_user_idx` (`userId`),
  INDEX `licenses_org_idx` (`organizationId`),
  INDEX `licenses_partner_idx` (`partnerId`),
  INDEX `licenses_status_idx` (`status`),
  INDEX `licenses_expires_idx` (`expiresAt`)
);
